FT_HourString : FT_HoursString );\n        var minuteString =  ( minutes  == 1 ? FT_MinuteString : FT_MinutesString );\n        if (hours == 0) {\n            return minutes + " " + minuteString;\n        }\n        if (minutes == 0) {\n          return hours + " " + hourString;\n Math.floor(FT_hoursLong);\n      var FT_minsLong = (FT_hoursLong - FT_hours) * 60;\n      var FT_mins = Math.floor(FT_minsLong);\n      var FT_secsLong = (FT_minsLong - FT_mins) * 60;\n      var FT_secs = Math.floor(FT_secsLong);\n          timerId = setTimeout(FT_getTime, 1000);\n      var ftCountdown = getTimeRemainingString( FT_days, FT_hours, FT_mins );\n      if }\n    \n    function FT_getCountdown(secondsLeft)\n    {\n      var FT_currentTime = new Date();\n      var FT_currentHours = FT_currentTime.getHours();\n      var FT_currentMins = FT_currentTime.getMinutes();\n      var FT_currentSecs = FT_currentTime.getSeconds();\n      FT_givenSeconds = FT_currentHours * 3600 + FT_currentMins * 60 + FT_currentSecs;\n      FT_givenSeconds += secondsLeft;\n      FT_getTime();\n    }\n    function FT_getTime()\n    {\n      var FT_newCurrentTime = new Date();\n      var FT_actualHours = FT_newCurrentTime.getHours();\n      if (FT_startedWithHour > FT_actualHours) {\n        FT_actualHours += 24;\n      }\n      var FT_actualMins = FT_newCurrentTime.getMinutes();\n      var FT_actualSecs = FT_newCurrentTime.getSeconds();\n dynamicImageMaxWidth = 679 ;\n    \n    dynamicImageMaxHeight = landingImage.naturalHeight;\n    dynamicImageMaxWidth = landingImage.naturalWidth;\n    \n    var aspectRatio = dynamicImageMaxWidth/dynamicImageMaxHeight;\n\n    var imageMaxHeight = containerHeight;\n    var imageMaxWidth = containerWidth;\n\n    if(!shouldAutoPlay && !true) {\n        imageMaxHeight = Math.min(imageMaxHeight, dynamicImageMaxHeight);\n        imageMaxWidth = Math.min(imageMaxWidth, dynamicImageMaxWidth);\n    }\n\n    \n    var useImageBlockLeftColCentering = false;\n    var class="a-expander-prompt">How does Amazon calculate star ratings?</span></a><div aria-expanded="false" class="a-expander-content a-expander-inline-content a-expander-inner" style="display:none">Amazon calculates a product\xe2\x80\x99s star ratings based on a machine learned model instead of a raw data average. The model takes into account factors including the age of a rating, whether the ratings are from verified purchasers, and factors that establish reviewer trustworthiness.</div></div></span>\n    <hr \n</a></div><span data-hook="review-date" class="a-size-base a-color-secondary review-date">Reviewed in the United States on September 23, 2019</span><div class="a-row a-spacing-mini review-data review-format-strip"><span data-hook="format-strip-linkless" class="a-color-secondary">Color: Matte Black</span><i class="a-icon a-icon-text-separator" role="img" aria-label="|"></i><span data-hook="avp-badge-linkless" class="a-size-mini a-color-state a-text-bold">Verified Purchase</span></div><div class="a-row a-spacing-small review-data"><span data-hook="review-body" class="a-size-base review-text"><div aria-live="polite" data-a-expander-name="review_text_read_more" data-a-expander-collapsed-height="300" class="a-expander-collapsed-height a-row a-expander-container a-expander-partial-collapse-container" style="max-height:300px"><div data-hook="review-collapsed" aria-expanded="false" class="a-expander-content reviewText review-text-content a-expander-partial-collapse-content">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n  \n    <span>When I preordered my iPhone 11, I also ordered several cases for it. I wanted to have a couple of options to choose from so that I\'d have a case on it immediately. This was one of three cases I got, and though I ended up returning it, I liked the design a lot.<br /><br />Pros:<br />- Snug fit for the phone<br />- Smooth edges & nice feel<br />- Lightweight<br />- Showcases colored phone nicely<br />- Side buttons easy to press<br />- All cutouts aligned<br /><br />Cons:<br />- Matte black edges are almost too smooth<br /><br />The only reason I knocked off a star in my rating is because the black edges on the matte black version are so smooth that they are almost hard to grip. I ended up going with a different Spigen case that has clear plastic around the edges where I am handling the phone because that material allows for a slightly better grip. I would imagine the Crystal Clear version of this (on the same listing) would be 5 stars.<br /><br />I really like the feel, weight, and look of this case. It nicely showcases my purple iPhone 11. All the cutouts are correct, and the side buttons are easy to press. The raised front edge and edge around the camera give a nice amount of additional protection. For the price, this is a great case.</span>\n  \n</div><div class="a-expander-header a-expander-partial-collapse-header"><div class="a-expander-content-fade"></div><a href="javascript:void(0)" a-expander-partial-collapse-content">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n  \n    <span>The case fits great. The TPU bumper around the edge feels good and solid and is grippy without feeling sticky.<br />The clear polycarbonate back is where I have a bit of a problem. It really shows fingerprints all of the time. I\xe2\x80\x99ve had a different clear PC case on another phone and rarely noticed fingerprints on it but maybe it\xe2\x80\x99s more a matter of having a black phone now instead of silver.<br />I also had to really scrub off some stickiness left from the protective films on the clear PC back.<br />Update: I got a Spigen Liquid Air Armor case and like that look and feel better. No fingerprints, less slippery, and being able to see the back of my black phone wasn\'t as exciting as I thought.</span>\n  \n</div><div class="a-expander-header class="a-size-base review-text"><div aria-live="polite" data-a-expander-name="review_text_read_more" data-a-expander-collapsed-height="300" class="a-expander-collapsed-height a-row a-expander-container a-expander-partial-collapse-container" style="max-height:300px"><div data-hook="review-collapsed" aria-expanded="false" class="a-expander-content reviewText review-text-content a-expander-partial-collapse-content">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n  \n    <span>I am pleased with the case as it\'s clear allowing the beautiful color of the iPhone 11 show through. Case has a good feel in the hand allowing me to grip the phone so it doesn\'t slip out. Buttons and access points function well. Laying the phone on the face, the slight raised edges of the case keep the glass from touching the table surface. When resting on it\'s back, there are 4 corner raised areas to keep the phone raised a bit and cameras do not touch the table surface. I have not experienced drop protection yet with the case, but the TPU edging should help. It\'s not the most rugged case out there, but for daily use at work and about at the cost, I like it very much. Previously, I used a wallet case which was functional adding space for credit cards, ID, and cash. But it hides the beauty of the phone and can be a bother when taking photos or videos. Taking photos with the simpler Spigen case is a breeze. Love the iPHone 11 wide angle lens and the zoom system transitions between lenses wonderfully.</span>\n  \n</div><div class="a-expander-header a-expander-partial-collapse-header"><div <span class="cr-original-review-content">Hallo,<br />da das iPhone 7 jetzt ausgewechselt ist, wurde f\xc3\xbcr das neue Ger\xc3\xa4t auch sofort wieder eine Spigen H\xc3\xbclle bestellt.<br /><br />Ich bin nun langj\xc3\xa4hriger und zufriedner Nutzer von iPhones und Spigen-H\xc3\xbcllen.<br />Deshalb hat die Wahl f\xc3\xbcr eine H\xc3\xbclle nicht lange gedauert und ich wurde nicht (b\xc3\xb6se) \xc3\xbcberrascht.<br />Die H\xc3\xbclle passt wie angegossen beim iPhone 11, sie liegt sehr eng an und wirkt  sehr stabil.<br />Der Lightning Anschluss, die Lautsprecher und Kamera-Aussparungen passen perfekt.<br />Auch die Tasten am iPhone lassen sich einwandfrei bedienen und sind nicht zu schwer zu dr\xc3\xbccken.<br /><br />Das Preis-Leistungsverh\xc3\xa4ltnis  stimmt hier einfach,  es sch\xc3\xbctzt das Handy und vor allem auch das Display durch den etwas h\xc3\xb6heren Rand perfekt.<br />Das Handy liegt durch die H\xc3\xbclle auch besser in der Hand und f\xc3\xbchlt sich nicht zu klobig an, durch die transparente R\xc3\xbcckseite schaut die sch\xc3\xb6ne R\xc3\xbcckseite des iPhones hervor.<br /><br />Ich w\xc3\xbcrde diese H\xc3\xbclle jedem iPhone Besitzer empfehlen, da hier einfach das Preis-Leistungsverh\xc3\xa4ltnis stimmt!<br /><br />Anbei befindet sich noch ein Foto der H\xc3\xbclle.<br /><br />Falls Sie diese Rezession hilfreich gefunden haben, w\xc3\xbcrde ich mich sehr \xc3\xbcber einen Like freuen.</span><span class="cr-translated-review-content aok-hidden"></span>\n  \n  \n</div><div class="a-expander-header aria-expanded="false" class="a-expander-content reviewText review-text-content a-expander-partial-collapse-content">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n  \n    <span>* I got this product on sale *<br />* My device has a skin applied to it on top of which the cover rests and THIS IS NOT A CAMOUFLAGED VERSION OF THE CASE *<br />* The back is transparent along with the black rims running along the camera space *<br /><br />Delivery : It was prompt as usual, delivered on the promised date.<br /><br />Packaging : The delivery box was well packed and unhampered. The product box itself is quite minimal and expressive.<br /><br />Product : The case is an absolute winner at that price. It does add some bulk to the device making it look a little chunky and heavy. Although being on the lighter side of the case spectrum, this case does add some solid feel to the phone. It surely adds grip in the corners while the hard plastic back is there to minimise the slipperiness off the glass. This case looks way, way better than the initial images rendered on the product page. The transparent back along with the black rims around the camera hump and all through out the edges adds some looks point to this device.<br />And yes this does support wireless charging :)<br /><br />Overall : At this price there\xe2\x80\x99s hardly any case out there offering better quality, overall value and appearance.<br /><br />Tap the helpful button to appreciate my effort of writing this review.   <span>This thing looks great on iPhone 11 with white back. Bought the transparent one. Fits tightly and feels rubbery which is a good thing, it kind of snaps to hand. Logo \xe2\x80\x9cSpigen\xe2\x80\x9d is hardly visible on a bottom left edge.<br />Another important bit is that it has a bit of bevel on the edge of screen. I still wait for screen protector but think case could be enough to protect screen from drops.<br />But the crap part was removal of protective film which is stuck from both inside and out of case. You can see from pics I had to use kitchen knife to remove it. Sticker did not help to lift it and I could not raise it with just my nail. Cannot give 5 stars just because of that.</span>\n  \n</div><div class="a-expander-header a-expander-partial-collapse-header"><div class="a-expander-content-fade"></div><a href="javascript:void(0)" a-text-bold">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n  \n    <span>Tough case for the iPhone 11</span>\n  \n</span></div><span data-hook="review-date" class="a-size-base a-color-secondary review-date">Reviewed in the United Kingdom on November 3, 2019</span><div class="a-row a-spacing-mini review-data review-format-strip"><span data-hook="format-strip-linkless" class="a-color-secondary">Color: Crystal Clear</span><i class="a-icon a-icon-text-separator" role="img" aria-label="|"></i><span data-hook="avp-badge-linkless" class="a-size-mini a-color-state a-text-bold">Verified Purchase</span></div><div class="a-row a-spacing-small review-data"><span data-hook="review-body" class="a-size-base review-text"><div aria-live="polite" data-a-expander-name="review_text_read_more" data-a-expander-collapsed-height="300" class="a-expander-collapsed-height a-row a-expander-container a-expander-partial-collapse-container" style="max-height:300px"><div data-hook="review-collapsed" aria-expanded="false" class="a-expander-content reviewText review-text-content a-expander-partial-collapse-content">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n  \n    <span>I\xe2\x80\x99ve always purchased Spigen phone cases, they are very resilient and can withstand hard knocks.  For that reason, I purchased the hybrid version again for my iPhone 11 and it fitted perfectly.  The phone itself is constructed from glass (back to front), so needed a tough protective hybrid case.  The case itself is light, slim, provides a reasonably good grip and doesn\xe2\x80\x99t make the phone bulky.  It has raised bezels to protect the screen and camera lenses, when the phone is placed on a flat surface.  Furthermore, it does not impact the wireless charging.  I have accidentally dropped the phone twice already in the street and it brilliantly protected my phone, not a single scratch or crack.<br />Excellent value for money and recommended.</span>\n It\xe2\x80\x99s slightly flexible but mostly solid. I actually bought this before the iPhone 11 release on Sept 20th and I am happy. Bear in mind, I have the Spigen case for my Iphone8 plus and it\xe2\x80\x99s held up real well. I went for the transparent look as it would quite frankly show off the Iphone11s design and not case it up. It\xe2\x80\x99s got a nice spigen logo on the side, quite subtle not overbearing. I\xe2\x80\x99ll try updating my review later but on first impressions, it\xe2\x80\x99s looking good.</span>\n  \n</div><div class="a-expander-header a-expander-partial-collapse-header"><div Lest selber.<br />Ja die Rezension gibt es auch bei der klaren H\xc3\xbclle. Habe beide:) Die Silikon/Kunstoff R\xc3\xa4nder f\xc3\xbchlen sich wertig an und haben Grip. Die Kn\xc3\xb6pfe sind gut gel\xc3\xb6st und lassen sich perfekt eindr\xc3\xbccken. Den Mute Regler kann man nat\xc3\xbcrlich nicht mehr mit dem bedienenden Zeigefinger nutzten. Ist aber auch egal. Dann nimmt man halt die andere Hand.<br />Die R\xc3\xbcckseite hat mich erst skeptisch gemacht aber ist durchdacht. Die Glas/Kunstoff R\xc3\xbcckseite ist minimal von dem IPhone getrennt, wodurch keine Kratzer oder diese punktuellen Anhaftungen entstehen k\xc3\xb6nnen.<br />Die R\xc3\xbcckseite der H\xc3\xbclle ist durch kleine Silikon Erh\xc3\xb6hungen an den Ecken vor Kratzern gesch\xc3\xbctzt.<br />Um die Kameras herum ist eine 2mm Erh\xc3\xb6hung um diese besonders zu sch\xc3\xbctzen.<br />Bin nicht daf\xc3\xbcr bezahlt worden.
